    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >90's Poland.  Potholed roads. 15% unemployment rate. Eurodance music.<br><br>And you, a simple country boy who loves to sit in the garage after nights. <br> <br>Key features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > buy OHV car, get rid of rust and dirt, paint and tune it, join &quot;Automobilklub&quot;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >build you own garage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >complete side quest chain to obtain Kredens car</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >build your buggy, cut and weld pipes in any shape you want and  take part in the races</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > paint your daily vehicle &quot;Odra&quot;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >deliver coal in  SMAR truck</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > build up your muscles on basement gym,  take part in weight lifting contest</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > eat sausage and &quot;oscypki&quot;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >make pickled cucumbers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >rob allotment gardens</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >cut off catalytic converter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >buy clothes on street market </p></li></ul>",
